				<td colspan="2"><span>Close, but where's the MT's bard? There still are encounters where resists and DSs matter. In many encounters your casters keep their distance while melee, of course, are in the fray. This makes it problematic for a bard to stay in range of both groups. So if you want a caster bard, make him a caster bard and have one tank/melee bard. A second bard will add more dps and utility then a third wiz.
