			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Zerkers at high levels are simply amazing DPS; Properly geared and AA'd they compete with high end rogues (in my experience).
<br />

<br />
Furthermore they can function as a tank/offtank almost as well as a pally/sk and their snap aggro (from stun axe/snare axe) is insane.
<br />

<br />
Dont underestimate the power of the zerk just b/c ya haven't met alot of them.
<br />

<br />
The only trouble w. them, is much like warriors; their usefullness is dependent almost entirely upon their gear/AA level.  A poorly geared; poorly AA'd zerk is indeed almost useless except as a WS puller or speed bump for a mob on route to own the cleric crew.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
